title: Jury deliberations to begin Wednesday in federal civil rights trial of 3 ex-officers involved in George Floyd's killing - CNN
content:
1. Jury deliberations to begin Wednesday in federal civil rights trial of 3 ex-officers involved in George Floyd's killing  CNN

description: Jury deliberations will begin Wednesday in the federal trial of three former Minneapolis police officers involved in George Floyd's 2020 killing, US District Court Judge Paul Magnuson said Tuesday.
